WEBVTT

00:00:00.320 --> 00:01:45.400

00:01:48.265 --> 00:01:51.345
QIHUANG CLINIC

00:01:56.905 --> 00:01:58.505
SIZHUKONG, ERMEN

00:02:15.985 --> 00:02:19.705
That person also told me
that in the afternoon of June 30th,

00:02:20.785 --> 00:02:23.025
those two people would head
to Qihuang Clinic.

00:02:23.585 --> 00:02:25.145
He told me to wait for them there.

00:02:26.065 --> 00:02:28.385
-A clinic?
-An unlicensed qigong center.

00:02:28.465 --> 00:02:29.545
It's probably sealed.

00:02:30.265 --> 00:02:31.345
What about the photo?

00:02:31.425 --> 00:02:33.385
I burned it.

00:02:33.985 --> 00:02:36.185
It's a rule in the gang.

00:02:38.145 --> 00:02:39.825
What does "make them disappear" mean?

00:02:39.905 --> 00:02:41.265
Kill them?

00:02:41.345 --> 00:02:42.945
I don't know either.

00:02:43.025 --> 00:02:45.945
He picked up the phone call and vanished.

00:02:47.065 --> 00:02:48.825
Officer He.

00:02:48.905 --> 00:02:51.105
I never intended to kill anyone.

00:02:51.185 --> 00:02:53.105
I just wanted to scare them,

00:02:53.185 --> 00:02:56.185
so they would leave Weiyang
and never come back again.

00:02:56.785 --> 00:02:58.705
That's disappearing, isn't it?

00:02:59.225 --> 00:03:02.305
I waited and waited, but no one ever came.

00:03:03.305 --> 00:03:05.145
So, I went out to take a peek.

00:03:06.545 --> 00:03:09.425
Then, I heard screams on the floor above.

00:03:10.105 --> 00:03:11.425
I then realized that the woman
and the old man

00:03:11.505 --> 00:03:13.185
didn't head to the 17th floor,

00:03:13.265 --> 00:03:14.425
but the 18th floor.

00:03:15.505 --> 00:03:17.705
I went to Pattia before.

00:03:17.785 --> 00:03:19.465
I know there is a secret door there.

00:03:19.985 --> 00:03:22.785
I figured they might
be hiding on the rooftop.

00:03:22.865 --> 00:03:25.265
But I walked around and didn't see them.

00:03:25.785 --> 00:03:26.705
Who gave you the keys?

00:03:29.305 --> 00:03:30.705
I used some tricks.

00:03:32.865 --> 00:03:34.905
Then, I wanted to get out of there.

00:03:37.345 --> 00:03:39.145
Then you people came to the 18th floor,

00:03:39.225 --> 00:03:41.745
group by group.

00:03:41.825 --> 00:03:43.945
I couldn't run away.

00:03:46.265 --> 00:03:49.185
I waited until the sun set.

00:03:51.985 --> 00:03:53.945
I couldn't stand it anymore.

00:03:54.025 --> 00:03:55.585
So, I let it out.

00:03:56.105 --> 00:03:58.265
I was all sweaty and dirty,

00:03:58.865 --> 00:04:00.145
and I thought

00:04:00.225 --> 00:04:02.585
I couldn't just suffer this for nothing.

00:04:02.665 --> 00:04:05.225
I must get the balance of the payment.

00:04:05.305 --> 00:04:07.985
I must show the gang how good I am.

00:04:13.905 --> 00:04:16.504
So, I bluffed.

00:04:17.105 --> 00:04:19.865
I grabbed a bag,
made myself a bloody cloak,

00:04:21.025 --> 00:04:22.745
and told everyone
that I had killed two people.

00:04:29.505 --> 00:04:30.825
Then, the blood in the bag…

00:04:30.905 --> 00:04:31.985
It's all chicken blood.

00:04:32.585 --> 00:04:33.985
Test it if you don't trust me.

00:04:34.065 --> 00:04:36.585
If it's human blood,
just shoot me on the spot.

00:04:47.425 --> 00:04:48.665
What were you doing in 407?

00:04:53.865 --> 00:04:55.265
Who gave you the job?

00:04:56.545 --> 00:04:57.505
I don't know who he is.

00:04:58.025 --> 00:05:00.545
-How much did he offer?
-Forty-thousand yuan.

00:05:00.625 --> 00:05:02.825
But he still owes me
the balance of 30,000 yuan.

00:05:02.905 --> 00:05:04.705
You can't even recognize him.

00:05:04.785 --> 00:05:06.625
How are you supposed to ask him to pay?

00:05:06.705 --> 00:05:10.025
He said he'd call me after the job.

00:05:10.105 --> 00:05:10.985
Buddy.

00:05:11.065 --> 00:05:13.305
You killed them.

00:05:13.825 --> 00:05:15.305
Why would he contact you?

00:05:16.145 --> 00:05:18.705
So that you can turn yourself in
to the police?

00:05:20.385 --> 00:05:21.825
Gosh.

00:05:24.065 --> 00:05:26.305
Did anyone see you when you did it?

00:05:29.745 --> 00:05:30.705
Answer me!

00:05:32.625 --> 00:05:33.865
I think

00:05:37.465 --> 00:05:39.185
I saw someone when I was leaving.

00:05:39.265 --> 00:05:40.345
You think?

00:05:56.865 --> 00:05:59.025
Idiot! And you can sleep
at night like this?

00:05:59.105 --> 00:06:01.705
Find that witness and silence him.

00:06:01.785 --> 00:06:05.345
That old man in 407 saw me.

00:06:05.985 --> 00:06:07.305
I had to silence him.

00:06:07.985 --> 00:06:10.105
Someone still owes me 30,000 yuan.

00:06:10.185 --> 00:06:12.385
If someone tells the police,

00:06:12.465 --> 00:06:14.265
I will be busted.

00:06:14.865 --> 00:06:17.065
I was very polite to him.

00:06:17.785 --> 00:06:19.225
Yes.

00:06:19.745 --> 00:06:21.665
He was quite polite.

00:06:22.185 --> 00:06:24.065
But really, I've never seen him before.

00:06:24.745 --> 00:06:26.225
Never.

00:06:26.305 --> 00:06:28.145
Last night,

00:06:28.225 --> 00:06:30.545
I was reading a detective novel in my bed.

00:06:30.625 --> 00:06:34.105
I was captivated by it, and it kept me up.

00:06:34.185 --> 00:06:35.185
I couldn't sleep,

00:06:35.265 --> 00:06:37.425
so I thought I could climb some stairs

00:06:37.505 --> 00:06:39.585
and sweat a little before I went to bed.

00:06:39.665 --> 00:06:42.345
As soon as I opened
the door to the staircase,

00:06:44.145 --> 00:06:46.545
I felt so drowsy.

00:06:46.625 --> 00:06:49.505
My eyelids were heavy.
I could barely keep them open.

00:06:49.585 --> 00:06:50.985
So, I went back to sleep.

00:06:51.065 --> 00:06:52.905
I didn't see anything.

00:06:54.185 --> 00:06:55.265
I didn't see him.

00:06:57.145 --> 00:06:59.345
You love to read detective novels?

00:06:59.425 --> 00:07:00.345
Yes.

00:07:00.425 --> 00:07:01.305
You too?

00:07:01.385 --> 00:07:02.345
Yes.

00:07:03.065 --> 00:07:04.785
We have the same hobby.

00:07:04.865 --> 00:07:06.625
What kind of detective novels?

00:07:06.705 --> 00:07:07.945
The classical European ones or--

00:07:09.545 --> 00:07:10.465
Du Mandun.

00:07:10.545 --> 00:07:12.985
If you didn't see Jin Manlang,
why did you call the police?

00:07:13.745 --> 00:07:16.505
I'm a fan of mysteries.

00:07:17.345 --> 00:07:18.465
Did you notice?

00:07:18.985 --> 00:07:22.345
Yesterday, someone disappeared
in a locked room on the 18th floor.

00:07:22.425 --> 00:07:25.825
Today, everyone is singing
that nursery song.

00:07:25.905 --> 00:07:30.385
Isn't that just like the prelude
to a murder in every detective novel?

00:07:31.305 --> 00:07:32.945
Speak plainly, please.

00:07:33.025 --> 00:07:34.785
Continue. I understand everything.

00:07:34.865 --> 00:07:36.705
-Okay. Listen.
-Sure.

00:07:36.785 --> 00:07:40.345
I thought the whole thing
could never be this simple.

00:07:40.425 --> 00:07:42.505
-At first…
-You didn't even see a shadow.

00:07:42.585 --> 00:07:43.945
Who says I didn't see anything?

00:07:44.545 --> 00:07:46.625
I saw her clearly.

00:07:46.705 --> 00:07:48.505
I saw the woman twice.

00:07:50.265 --> 00:07:52.225
I saw her carrying… Like…

00:07:53.105 --> 00:07:55.145
Relax. Tell us one by one.

00:07:58.025 --> 00:07:59.505
I first saw her

00:08:00.225 --> 00:08:03.065
in the morning several days ago.

00:08:03.585 --> 00:08:07.105
Right at the corner of the staircase.

00:08:17.905 --> 00:08:21.505
The second time I saw her was yesterday.

00:08:22.105 --> 00:08:26.625
I was playing gateball
at the park with Meng and Wang.

00:08:26.705 --> 00:08:30.185
I saw the woman walking by
while carrying an old man.

00:08:30.265 --> 00:08:32.065
She looked exactly like the woman

00:08:32.144 --> 00:08:34.945
I had met on the staircase
several days ago.

00:08:35.024 --> 00:08:36.465
Are you sure they were identical?

00:08:39.065 --> 00:08:40.705
Try to recall.

00:08:40.784 --> 00:08:43.065
Did anything stand out
when you saw the woman?

00:08:43.585 --> 00:08:45.345
-Anything that stood out?
-Yes.

00:08:56.665 --> 00:08:59.505
She had medical patches on her wrists.

00:08:59.585 --> 00:09:01.665
Over here and over here.

00:09:05.665 --> 00:09:09.985
These are probably marks
left by medical patches.

00:09:13.785 --> 00:09:14.665
It matches.

00:09:15.265 --> 00:09:16.945
How so?

00:09:17.025 --> 00:09:18.425
The medical patch has her name on it?

00:09:20.025 --> 00:09:21.385
This is an important lead.

00:09:21.465 --> 00:09:23.545
What kind of woman would use
medical patches on her wrists?

00:09:23.625 --> 00:09:25.465
It must have something to do with her job.

00:09:26.105 --> 00:09:28.065
That's just your opinion.

00:09:28.145 --> 00:09:30.945
I think she might have injured
her wrists while she carried things.

00:09:31.025 --> 00:09:33.025
Or she might have a scar
that she didn't want anyone to see.

00:09:33.105 --> 00:09:34.425
The possibilities are endless.

00:09:34.505 --> 00:09:36.505
Yes. You're absolutely right.

00:09:36.585 --> 00:09:38.985
All these possibilities
are possible clues to this murder.

00:09:39.065 --> 00:09:40.985
Must you get us a murder case?

00:09:41.065 --> 00:09:42.705
Someone has hired a man to kill them.

00:09:42.785 --> 00:09:44.265
How is this not a murder?

00:09:45.745 --> 00:09:48.625
Officer, is this truly a murder?

00:10:03.625 --> 00:10:07.025
We analyzed the blood
in the bag and on the rooftop.

00:10:07.105 --> 00:10:08.145
It's not human blood.

00:10:08.905 --> 00:10:11.545
The saliva sample from the cigarette butt
matches Jin Manlang.

00:10:14.865 --> 00:10:17.785
It seems like someone
has tried so hard for nothing.

00:10:17.865 --> 00:10:21.385
They probably hope the witnesses are lying
so that they can continue investigating.

00:10:23.305 --> 00:10:24.465
I know they are not lying.

00:10:24.545 --> 00:10:25.545
How do you know?

00:10:25.625 --> 00:10:27.505
Eyes are the window to your soul.

00:10:27.585 --> 00:10:29.465
If you look to the left when you speak,
it means that you're recalling.

00:10:29.545 --> 00:10:31.065
If you look to the right,
it means you're making things up.

00:10:31.145 --> 00:10:33.225
When Jin Manlang and Mr. Du were speaking,

00:10:33.305 --> 00:10:34.785
they were looking to the left.

00:10:35.465 --> 00:10:36.585
What about the photo?

00:10:38.025 --> 00:10:39.865
I burned it.

00:10:43.385 --> 00:10:45.065
I first saw her

00:10:48.465 --> 00:10:49.745
in the…

00:10:50.265 --> 00:10:52.785
They did not have
the telltale sign of lying.

00:10:58.585 --> 00:11:00.625
Smarty pants who like to lecture.

00:11:00.705 --> 00:11:02.225
They did not lie,

00:11:02.305 --> 00:11:04.185
but that doesn't mean
the two missing people

00:11:04.265 --> 00:11:05.585
are not in danger.

00:11:06.705 --> 00:11:08.105
Can you two stop arguing?

00:11:09.705 --> 00:11:11.185
I analyzed everything in the box.

00:11:11.265 --> 00:11:12.305
Nothing new.

00:11:12.385 --> 00:11:14.985
Keep it or return it, it's your call.

00:11:16.225 --> 00:11:17.425
I still have work to do.

00:11:25.025 --> 00:11:27.625
THE GREEK COFFIN MYSTERY

00:11:38.305 --> 00:11:41.145
MISSING PERSON

00:12:05.065 --> 00:12:06.105
MISSING PERSON

00:12:06.185 --> 00:12:09.305
Why is this poster still here?

00:12:10.305 --> 00:12:11.505
Isn't it weird?

00:12:12.065 --> 00:12:13.625
Let me show you something weirder.

00:12:25.705 --> 00:12:28.185
‎DEMOLITION

00:12:35.585 --> 00:12:36.625
Does this look familiar to you?

00:12:41.345 --> 00:12:43.985
Does this belong to Jin Manlang?

00:12:51.865 --> 00:12:54.865
I returned everything back then.

00:12:54.945 --> 00:12:57.865
This mooncake box belongs to Wolfie.

00:12:59.025 --> 00:13:01.705
This detective novel belongs to Du Mandun.

00:13:02.905 --> 00:13:07.345
Why are their things
kept together in the same place?

00:13:08.465 --> 00:13:09.705
And look at the poster.

00:13:10.505 --> 00:13:14.025
The paper and the ink are both new.

00:13:16.065 --> 00:13:17.505
Weird, isn't it?

00:13:18.105 --> 00:13:19.345
It has been so many years.

00:13:20.665 --> 00:13:23.705
I never believed
that Yuanlongli was haunted.

00:13:24.425 --> 00:13:25.265
YUXI CIGARETTE

00:13:25.345 --> 00:13:27.305
Someone must be behind all of this.

00:13:59.945 --> 00:14:01.145
407.

00:14:01.665 --> 00:14:03.225
Du Mandun's unit.

00:14:03.745 --> 00:14:05.105
He moved out several months ago.

00:14:29.625 --> 00:14:30.945
So, it was all a false alarm.

00:14:34.585 --> 00:14:38.185
Du Mandun moved out,
but he didn't take his books.

00:14:47.825 --> 00:14:50.545
I remember he was quite invested

00:14:50.625 --> 00:14:52.505
in the missing persons case back then.

00:14:52.585 --> 00:14:54.945
He even discussed some conspiracies
or locked rooms with you.

00:14:55.665 --> 00:14:56.865
Sir,

00:14:56.945 --> 00:14:58.425
ever since we set foot into Yuanlongli,

00:14:58.505 --> 00:15:00.505
you've been mentioning
that particular case.

00:15:00.585 --> 00:15:02.385
What does it have to do
with the missing kid?

00:15:03.105 --> 00:15:05.505
It has everything to do with it.
They are both missing person cases.

00:15:05.585 --> 00:15:06.505
So?

00:15:07.585 --> 00:15:09.665
So, we're looking for them.

00:15:10.825 --> 00:15:12.025
Sir,

00:15:12.105 --> 00:15:13.545
I came to Weiyang
to write the lesson plan,

00:15:13.625 --> 00:15:15.065
and my schedule is tight enough.

00:15:17.425 --> 00:15:18.945
Three floors left.

00:15:19.025 --> 00:15:20.545
You gave me your word.

00:15:20.625 --> 00:15:22.705
Now keep your promise.

00:15:33.425 --> 00:15:34.505
Let's go.

00:15:35.225 --> 00:15:36.185
Let's go.

00:15:45.785 --> 00:15:48.465
WEIYANG PUBLIC SECURITY BUREAU
NANSHAN BRANCH

00:16:00.865 --> 00:16:01.705
I already signed.

00:16:01.785 --> 00:16:02.985
Please sign it, too.

00:16:04.865 --> 00:16:06.425
CRIMINAL CASE REGISTRATION FORM

00:16:06.505 --> 00:16:08.705
Since you always go to Qu Dahai,
ask him to sign it.

00:16:09.305 --> 00:16:10.665
He doesn't have the power.

00:16:11.985 --> 00:16:12.865
Neither do I.

00:16:13.465 --> 00:16:15.545
Don't worry. After you sign it,
I'll be in charge of it.

00:16:15.625 --> 00:16:17.905
You're a rookie. How
can you be in charge of it?

00:16:17.985 --> 00:16:20.105
Our priority now is not to file a case.

00:16:20.185 --> 00:16:22.345
It's to find those two people.

00:16:31.745 --> 00:16:33.425
If you won't sign the registration form,

00:16:33.505 --> 00:16:34.545
can you sign this?

00:16:34.625 --> 00:16:35.465
EVIDENCE SUBPOENA REQUEST FORM

00:16:36.465 --> 00:16:37.305
What is this?

00:16:38.105 --> 00:16:39.825
The woman used medical patches.

00:16:39.905 --> 00:16:41.745
I want to check the hospital records

00:16:41.825 --> 00:16:43.905
to see if someone
injured their wrists lately.

00:16:45.665 --> 00:16:47.625
You don't have
any real-life experience, do you?

00:16:47.705 --> 00:16:49.785
Do you think

00:16:49.865 --> 00:16:51.345
they will go to the hospital
for a small injury like this?

00:16:52.625 --> 00:16:54.705
Where else could she
have gotten the patches?

00:16:54.785 --> 00:16:55.985
In a pharmacy.

00:16:56.065 --> 00:16:57.225
In a clinic.

00:16:57.305 --> 00:16:59.545
Many people are selling
common medications.

00:16:59.625 --> 00:17:01.545
Following your method, I can sign it,

00:17:01.625 --> 00:17:04.145
and you still won't
find anything after years.

00:17:04.224 --> 00:17:05.424
Then, how should we proceed?

00:17:05.505 --> 00:17:07.825
Put up posters and wait on the bench?

00:17:07.905 --> 00:17:09.625
Are you lecturing me right now?

00:17:09.704 --> 00:17:12.025
At least I caught someone
after waiting the whole day.

00:17:12.105 --> 00:17:13.625
What did you find?

00:17:13.704 --> 00:17:15.265
Chicken blood?

00:17:15.345 --> 00:17:17.585
Duck blood can be added to a hotpot.
But chicken blood? It's useless.

00:17:17.665 --> 00:17:18.905
Enough.

00:17:18.985 --> 00:17:20.745
-Will you sign it or not?
-No!

00:17:25.545 --> 00:17:26.625
Criminal department.

00:17:26.704 --> 00:17:27.625
Dad!

00:17:30.225 --> 00:17:31.825
Yes. It's me.

00:17:32.865 --> 00:17:34.185
You haven't come back in so long.

00:17:34.265 --> 00:17:36.745
It's getting harder to see you now.

00:17:37.865 --> 00:17:39.665
I'll come back soon.

00:17:39.745 --> 00:17:40.825
Again?

00:17:40.905 --> 00:17:44.185
Your soon is getting absurdly long.

00:17:44.265 --> 00:17:45.865
Kiddo,

00:17:46.425 --> 00:17:48.705
I recently ran into a troublemaker.

00:17:48.785 --> 00:17:49.865
He keeps pestering me.

00:17:50.545 --> 00:17:52.105
Then, buy me a bottle of Coke.

00:17:52.185 --> 00:17:54.145
Don't tell Mom.

00:17:54.225 --> 00:17:55.545
Sure.

00:17:56.065 --> 00:17:57.985
Wait. Mom wants to talk to you.

00:17:58.505 --> 00:17:59.345
Xiaohe.

00:17:59.425 --> 00:18:00.385
Go back to your room.

00:18:00.465 --> 00:18:01.865
He Yuanhang, where are you?

00:18:03.665 --> 00:18:05.265
I'm working now.

00:18:05.345 --> 00:18:07.825
I need to work hard to impress my boss.

00:18:07.905 --> 00:18:09.865
That way, I can stay
in the criminal department.

00:18:09.945 --> 00:18:12.145
Are you trying to get back
to the police station again?

00:18:12.985 --> 00:18:15.185
Who says that? That's impossible.

00:18:15.265 --> 00:18:16.905
I met Qu Dahai today.

00:18:16.985 --> 00:18:18.105
He told me that.

00:18:18.185 --> 00:18:20.705
-He said you'd return next week.
-Qu Dahai.

00:18:21.305 --> 00:18:23.865
Listen. He's trying to break us up.

00:18:23.945 --> 00:18:26.825
He can't wait to return
to the police station.

00:18:27.545 --> 00:18:28.905
What? He Yuanhang!

00:18:28.985 --> 00:18:29.985
It's noisy here.

00:18:30.065 --> 00:18:31.065
The lines are mixed up.

00:18:31.145 --> 00:18:34.425
-Officer He said only six days left till…
-Till I catch…

00:18:34.505 --> 00:18:36.345
Wait. It's noisy here.

00:18:36.425 --> 00:18:38.105
Only six days left till he goes back to…

00:18:38.745 --> 00:18:40.065
Give me a moment.

00:18:45.625 --> 00:18:46.465
Don't worry.

00:18:46.545 --> 00:18:49.945
I'll work hard to stay
in the criminal department.

00:18:50.025 --> 00:18:51.305
I have to hang up now.

00:18:51.385 --> 00:18:52.905
I have a meeting soon. Okay.

00:18:54.145 --> 00:18:56.505
Getting bolder now, huh?

00:19:11.985 --> 00:19:12.825
Let's go.

00:19:12.905 --> 00:19:14.585
You go ahead. I need to work.

00:19:14.665 --> 00:19:15.865
Who says it's not about work?

00:19:15.945 --> 00:19:16.985
We have a new lead.

00:19:18.025 --> 00:19:18.905
Hey!

00:19:18.985 --> 00:19:19.865
Wait for me.

00:19:24.825 --> 00:19:25.905
Where are my shoes?

00:19:30.585 --> 00:19:32.065
You have five minutes

00:19:32.145 --> 00:19:33.705
to get yourself some new outfits
at the night market.

00:19:52.705 --> 00:19:53.545
Sir, buy some leather shoes.

00:19:53.625 --> 00:19:55.225
They are all genuine leather. Take a look.

00:19:55.305 --> 00:19:56.345
We have a clearance sale today.

00:19:56.425 --> 00:19:58.105
Everything is cheap. Trust me.

00:19:58.185 --> 00:20:00.065
Sir, you have great taste.

00:20:02.265 --> 00:20:04.225
Double Fish Heels. They are branded.

00:20:04.305 --> 00:20:05.625
Are they for your girlfriend?

00:20:08.185 --> 00:20:09.145
Sir.

00:20:09.665 --> 00:20:10.905
Come. Take a look.

00:20:11.425 --> 00:20:13.065
I also have stirrup pants. Get them too.

00:20:13.145 --> 00:20:15.625
Blue and red, as beautiful as you get.

00:20:17.585 --> 00:20:19.145
Sir, help me out, will you?

00:20:19.225 --> 00:20:20.465
I'll forever remember your generosity.

00:20:50.905 --> 00:20:51.905
Did you gain some common sense?

00:20:59.865 --> 00:21:00.905
Boat orchids.

00:21:00.985 --> 00:21:02.185
You splurged.

00:21:03.705 --> 00:21:04.545
It's to compensate someone.

00:21:06.945 --> 00:21:08.265
Compensate someone?

00:21:31.625 --> 00:21:34.585
You're somehow attached
to these old sandals?

00:21:37.745 --> 00:21:39.585
It's to compensate someone too.

00:21:39.665 --> 00:21:41.025
It's to compensate someone too?

00:21:41.105 --> 00:21:42.465
You have only worked for two days.

00:21:42.545 --> 00:21:43.425
You didn't earn anything,

00:21:43.505 --> 00:21:44.505
but you have to compensate
for losses already.

00:21:45.305 --> 00:21:46.145
Well done.

00:21:55.745 --> 00:21:58.025
Oh. Guess what I saw in the night market.

00:21:59.265 --> 00:22:01.545
The blue leather heels
worn by the missing woman.

00:22:02.065 --> 00:22:03.465
They are called Double Fish Heels.

00:22:03.545 --> 00:22:05.665
A renowned brand, apparently.
Expensive too.

00:22:05.745 --> 00:22:07.065
They come in different colors.

00:22:07.145 --> 00:22:09.825
Red, black, and even white.

00:22:11.465 --> 00:22:14.625
Why didn't you buy something
for your intelligence?

00:22:14.705 --> 00:22:17.585
Branded goods in a night market?
How authentic can they be?

00:22:26.025 --> 00:22:26.945
Hey. What are you doing?

00:22:28.585 --> 00:22:31.025
Don't touch it.
If you break it, I'll be in trouble.

00:22:34.465 --> 00:22:36.265
Is this your daughter's?

00:22:37.065 --> 00:22:38.345
Yes.

00:22:38.425 --> 00:22:39.865
How old is she?

00:22:41.465 --> 00:22:43.465
Eight years old. Year 3.

00:22:44.705 --> 00:22:48.185
Is she the reason why you don't want
to stay in the criminal department?

00:22:50.425 --> 00:22:51.985
I know it wouldn't be because of you.

00:22:52.705 --> 00:22:53.985
Stop asking questions.

00:22:54.625 --> 00:22:55.665
It's none of your business.

00:22:59.185 --> 00:23:00.185
You studied in Beijing.

00:23:00.265 --> 00:23:02.185
But you are assigned to Weiyang.

00:23:02.265 --> 00:23:03.425
Is your family okay with it?

00:23:05.025 --> 00:23:06.145
You checked my file.

00:23:07.105 --> 00:23:08.105
I didn't.

00:23:08.185 --> 00:23:10.105
But when Captain Feng
gave me an apprentice,

00:23:10.185 --> 00:23:11.105
I had to check what I'd be getting.

00:23:11.185 --> 00:23:12.465
Let me reiterate.

00:23:12.545 --> 00:23:14.265
-I am not your apprentice.
-All right.

00:23:14.905 --> 00:23:16.425
Won't you get sick of nagging,
my dear apprentice?

00:23:16.505 --> 00:23:17.345
I…

00:23:23.865 --> 00:23:26.345
You look so pampered.

00:23:26.865 --> 00:23:28.625
Your family must be rich.

00:23:29.705 --> 00:23:31.505
What do your parents do?

00:23:44.785 --> 00:23:51.665
SHANCHENG HOTPOT

00:24:11.305 --> 00:24:12.545
He's quite handsome,

00:24:12.625 --> 00:24:15.825
but his fashion sense is a bit lacking.

00:24:15.905 --> 00:24:17.905
He is dressed like an old man.

00:24:21.985 --> 00:24:24.345
I'll bring some drinks over.

00:24:27.025 --> 00:24:27.865
What do you want?

00:24:28.945 --> 00:24:31.305
Whatever you bring me.

00:24:37.385 --> 00:24:39.905
I didn't know
it was your number on the poster.

00:24:40.505 --> 00:24:42.425
If I had known it,
I wouldn't have called you.

00:24:44.665 --> 00:24:46.185
I'm just helping out.

00:24:46.265 --> 00:24:48.065
Their relatives are eager to find them.

00:24:48.585 --> 00:24:49.625
Relatives?

00:24:58.745 --> 00:24:59.585
Thanks, cutie.

00:25:00.505 --> 00:25:01.985
You're… You're welcome.

00:25:05.665 --> 00:25:07.185
MISSING PERSON

00:25:07.265 --> 00:25:08.625
Do you know them?

00:25:14.105 --> 00:25:17.225
The woman on the poster was my colleague.

00:25:21.105 --> 00:25:22.425
Colleagues?

00:25:22.505 --> 00:25:24.825
What's her name? What kind of work?

00:25:25.625 --> 00:25:27.185
Ex-colleagues.

00:25:28.185 --> 00:25:29.025
Her name is Mengmeng.

00:25:29.825 --> 00:25:31.345
What kind of work?

00:25:33.945 --> 00:25:34.865
A massage parlor.

00:25:37.345 --> 00:25:39.865
No wonder she used medical patches.

00:25:41.985 --> 00:25:44.105
What's her surname? Her full name, please.

00:25:44.185 --> 00:25:46.305
Mengmeng is just a nickname.

00:25:46.385 --> 00:25:49.785
Masseuses never use their real names.

00:25:50.625 --> 00:25:51.945
Ignore him.

00:25:52.025 --> 00:25:53.945
He's just a rookie who knows nothing.

00:25:54.025 --> 00:25:56.105
Just share your information with me.

00:25:56.985 --> 00:25:59.105
Cutie. Let me tell you the truth.

00:25:59.905 --> 00:26:01.025
It's a massage parlor,

00:26:01.105 --> 00:26:03.145
but we do all sorts of things there.

00:26:03.225 --> 00:26:05.385
So, the girls there
are from other regions.

00:26:05.465 --> 00:26:07.505
Mengmeng is the only local there.

00:26:08.025 --> 00:26:09.545
I only know

00:26:09.625 --> 00:26:12.185
that her father is quite sick.

00:26:12.265 --> 00:26:13.745
She can't leave Weiyang.

00:26:14.785 --> 00:26:15.865
Have you seen her father?

00:26:17.705 --> 00:26:20.265
I guess it was the guy she was carrying.

00:26:22.025 --> 00:26:24.145
Does Mengmeng have other relatives?

00:26:27.785 --> 00:26:29.705
Didn't you tell me her relatives
were looking for her?

00:26:31.465 --> 00:26:33.705
Police officers and citizens are a family.

00:26:33.785 --> 00:26:36.545
I can't find her relatives,
but I'll help them find her first.

00:26:37.905 --> 00:26:39.665
Officer He. The police can't find them.

00:26:39.745 --> 00:26:41.305
Let alone a citizen like me.

00:26:46.665 --> 00:26:48.985
Where is the parlor?

00:26:49.065 --> 00:26:50.225
What is the name?

00:26:50.305 --> 00:26:51.465
Ask him.

00:26:51.545 --> 00:26:52.945
He raided the place.

00:26:57.785 --> 00:26:58.865
Pattia.

00:26:59.425 --> 00:27:01.785
Cutie. You've been there before?

00:27:02.385 --> 00:27:03.745
How come I've never seen you?

00:27:03.825 --> 00:27:06.545
No, not at all. I… I just came to Weiyang.

00:27:08.585 --> 00:27:11.905
I just want to know if Mengmeng
is close to anyone else.

00:27:11.985 --> 00:27:14.065
She is the quiet type.

00:27:14.145 --> 00:27:15.465
Quite dull.

00:27:15.545 --> 00:27:17.785
When she was not working,
she would make small talk with me.

00:27:19.465 --> 00:27:21.985
A rich man often asked for her.

00:27:22.065 --> 00:27:24.425
Sometimes, he would take her with him.

00:27:26.465 --> 00:27:28.185
Rich man? What's his name?

00:27:28.785 --> 00:27:30.105
Sun, I think.

00:27:30.185 --> 00:27:32.905
I don't know his name.

00:27:35.505 --> 00:27:36.625
Try to recall.

00:27:36.705 --> 00:27:38.625
He asked for Mengmeng, not me.

00:27:38.705 --> 00:27:41.545
Besides, who uses their real name
in this kind of place?

00:27:43.025 --> 00:27:45.065
Do you know where Mengmeng went afterward?

00:27:45.945 --> 00:27:48.945
She went to a foot massage parlor

00:27:49.025 --> 00:27:51.185
in Tenglong Street.

00:27:51.785 --> 00:27:54.705
I think it's called… Muse.

00:28:14.625 --> 00:28:18.185
People in my line of work
are used to moving frequently.

00:28:18.705 --> 00:28:20.265
Many went missing too,

00:28:21.145 --> 00:28:23.305
but no one cares.

00:28:32.905 --> 00:28:35.865
I don't care if others care about it,
but we will see it through.

00:28:35.945 --> 00:28:37.425
Don't worry about it.

00:28:41.145 --> 00:28:42.625
Allow me to thank you
on behalf of Mengmeng.

00:28:47.025 --> 00:28:48.305
No need. It's our job.

00:28:57.385 --> 00:28:58.705
Dig in. It's on me today.

00:29:00.025 --> 00:29:01.465
What do you like to eat?

00:29:02.305 --> 00:29:03.385
Anything.

00:29:03.465 --> 00:29:04.305
Then, I'll add everything in.

00:29:09.345 --> 00:29:13.145
SHANCHENG HOTPOT

00:29:19.585 --> 00:29:21.345
Thank you for providing
crucial information.

00:29:21.425 --> 00:29:22.905
We can help you claim the reward.

00:29:23.985 --> 00:29:25.585
I don't want your money.

00:29:26.545 --> 00:29:28.745
Remember. You owe me a meal of hotpot,

00:29:28.825 --> 00:29:29.825
cutie.

00:29:31.985 --> 00:29:33.025
Wait.

00:29:34.905 --> 00:29:37.785
Is your father Su Qingyou?

00:29:48.265 --> 00:29:51.065
This must be yours.

00:30:00.185 --> 00:30:01.985
I've been looking for this photo.

00:30:02.065 --> 00:30:03.105
Where did you find it?

00:30:04.025 --> 00:30:06.745
Eighteenth floor of Yuanlongli.
Where Pattia was.

00:30:09.625 --> 00:30:11.145
SU QINGYOU

00:30:22.305 --> 00:30:23.465
Cutie,

00:30:23.545 --> 00:30:25.945
when you're free,
you must visit the parlor.

00:30:26.025 --> 00:30:27.585
I'll give you a nice surprise.

00:30:28.385 --> 00:30:29.425
See you.

00:30:34.505 --> 00:30:37.425
Are you here to investigate
the case or to flirt?

00:30:38.465 --> 00:30:39.505
Go now.

00:30:40.665 --> 00:30:41.745
Where to?

00:30:41.825 --> 00:30:43.025
To find the surprise.

00:30:48.865 --> 00:30:51.505
MUSE FOOT MASSAGE

00:30:59.385 --> 00:31:00.345
‎-Sir!
‎-Dear sir!

00:31:00.945 --> 00:31:03.625
‎-Come on in!
‎-We waited for so long.

00:31:06.145 --> 00:31:08.065
You will go in through the main entrance.

00:31:08.145 --> 00:31:09.065
I'll take the rear entrance.

00:31:09.145 --> 00:31:11.065
If something happens, we'll surround them.

00:31:14.785 --> 00:31:15.705
Wait.

00:31:15.785 --> 00:31:18.825
When you're inside,
do you know what to say?

00:31:18.905 --> 00:31:20.785
Say what? I'll speak
like I normally would.

00:31:22.985 --> 00:31:24.265
I know.

00:31:25.065 --> 00:31:26.945
Since you're so approachable,

00:31:27.025 --> 00:31:28.745
why did you ask me to go in?

00:31:29.265 --> 00:31:30.945
I'm worried they might recognize me.

00:31:36.025 --> 00:31:37.345
Get that out of your mind!

00:31:37.425 --> 00:31:39.065
Don't you know what I did?

00:31:39.145 --> 00:31:40.345
Go now.

00:31:52.905 --> 00:31:56.465
MUSE FOOT MASSAGE

00:32:03.385 --> 00:32:05.465
Be patient. It's fine,
even if they are new.

00:32:05.985 --> 00:32:08.465
There are some over there.
A few girls over there.

00:32:10.825 --> 00:32:12.145
Hi, Mister.

00:32:12.225 --> 00:32:13.185
First time here?

00:32:14.985 --> 00:32:15.905
Yes.

00:32:17.905 --> 00:32:19.185
Come in.

00:32:19.265 --> 00:32:20.985
-Dear sir!
-Sir! Is it your first time here?

00:32:21.065 --> 00:32:22.145
You want something?

00:32:22.225 --> 00:32:23.185
Don't be shy.

00:32:23.265 --> 00:32:25.105
Yes, don't be shy.

00:32:25.825 --> 00:32:27.625
The price is over there.
Pick anything you like.

00:32:40.985 --> 00:32:42.465
Anything will do.

00:32:44.865 --> 00:32:45.745
Anything will do?

00:32:45.825 --> 00:32:48.385
So which service then? Take a look.

00:32:49.945 --> 00:32:50.865
You know what?

00:32:51.705 --> 00:32:52.985
I want Mengmeng to massage me.

00:32:56.625 --> 00:32:57.465
Mengmeng?

00:32:57.545 --> 00:33:00.305
She is sick today.

00:33:00.385 --> 00:33:01.825
She took sick leave.

00:33:03.265 --> 00:33:05.665
Pick another one.
The girls here are very friendly.

00:33:05.745 --> 00:33:07.065
Exactly.

00:33:07.145 --> 00:33:08.105
Pick another one.

00:33:10.505 --> 00:33:12.305
Where is your boss?

00:33:14.465 --> 00:33:15.305
Behind.

00:33:16.265 --> 00:33:17.345
I'll get her for you.

00:33:17.425 --> 00:33:18.425
Okay.

00:33:18.945 --> 00:33:20.225
Give me a second.

00:33:22.385 --> 00:33:23.385
Give me a second.

00:33:27.265 --> 00:33:28.265
Raid!

00:33:28.345 --> 00:33:30.065
Raid! Raid!

00:33:30.145 --> 00:33:32.265
Raid!

00:33:36.905 --> 00:33:37.865
ROOM 3

00:33:47.185 --> 00:33:49.105
Pervert! Pervert!

00:33:49.185 --> 00:33:50.585
Pervert!

00:34:00.545 --> 00:34:01.345
Stop!

00:34:04.425 --> 00:34:05.265
You still won't stop?

00:34:18.264 --> 00:34:19.465
Officer.

00:34:19.545 --> 00:34:22.304
I just washed my feet. They are clean.

00:34:24.705 --> 00:34:25.985
Ms. Zhao.

00:34:26.065 --> 00:34:28.865
I spilled the feet water
on his face just now.

00:34:29.545 --> 00:34:30.705
Is it funny?

00:34:31.865 --> 00:34:33.185
Tell me.

00:34:33.264 --> 00:34:35.705
When did all of you last see Mengmeng?

00:34:36.344 --> 00:34:37.665
I don't know.

00:34:39.945 --> 00:34:42.545
She stopped coming to work three days ago.

00:34:43.865 --> 00:34:44.985
Why?

00:34:45.945 --> 00:34:47.705
Did she run into trouble
on her last day here?

00:34:47.784 --> 00:34:48.744
I don't know.

00:34:50.065 --> 00:34:51.585
What could possibly happen here?

00:34:51.665 --> 00:34:54.264
And how would I know
why she stopped coming to work?

00:34:55.145 --> 00:34:58.145
Did she meet any clients
on her last day here?

00:35:00.105 --> 00:35:01.865
I don't know.

00:35:01.945 --> 00:35:03.185
No one picked her.

00:35:03.265 --> 00:35:05.185
She didn't earn anything,
so she stopped coming.

00:35:05.265 --> 00:35:06.105
You…

00:35:09.345 --> 00:35:10.945
First, you said you didn't know.

00:35:11.025 --> 00:35:12.745
Now, you said no one picked her.

00:35:12.825 --> 00:35:15.145
So, do you know something or not?

00:35:15.825 --> 00:35:17.065
Sir.

00:35:18.625 --> 00:35:20.305
"I don't know" is my catchphrase.

00:35:21.025 --> 00:35:24.105
Mengmeng and I are colleagues.

00:35:24.185 --> 00:35:25.225
She's like my subordinate.

00:35:25.825 --> 00:35:29.505
Why would she tell me about her troubles?

00:35:30.185 --> 00:35:31.065
Ask them if you don't trust me.

00:35:31.145 --> 00:35:33.945
Would you come to me
if you run into trouble?

00:35:37.625 --> 00:35:38.785
See?

00:35:45.705 --> 00:35:46.705
All right.

00:35:47.545 --> 00:35:49.825
Surely, you must know
Mengmeng's real name.

00:35:51.865 --> 00:35:53.145
Of course.

00:35:59.905 --> 00:36:01.385
NRIC PHOTOCOPY

00:36:06.665 --> 00:36:09.385
XU MENG

00:36:09.465 --> 00:36:15.385
DAJIANCHANG NEIGHBORHOOD

00:36:17.705 --> 00:36:21.185
Why didn't you tell the others
to raid the foot massage parlor?

00:36:21.985 --> 00:36:23.385
You know nothing.

00:36:23.945 --> 00:36:26.345
It's not the time to retrieve the net yet.

00:36:27.105 --> 00:36:29.585
Let's wait till we find
Xu Meng and her father.

00:36:50.785 --> 00:36:51.825
Stop searching.

00:36:52.585 --> 00:36:54.225
It should be that unit.

00:36:57.985 --> 00:37:03.345
DIE

00:37:25.825 --> 00:37:26.945
A putrid stench.

00:37:32.385 --> 00:37:33.545
Corpse?

00:37:35.425 --> 00:37:36.625
Not sure.

00:37:44.665 --> 00:37:46.185
It's locked from the inside.

00:37:46.265 --> 00:37:48.065
I can't open it without the keys.

00:38:00.705 --> 00:38:02.345
Don't just stand there.

00:38:02.425 --> 00:38:03.785
Call for backup

00:38:04.385 --> 00:38:05.905
and ask them to break the door.

00:38:12.265 --> 00:38:13.305
Do you know how to do this?

00:38:13.905 --> 00:38:16.945
We learned how to pick locks at school.

00:38:17.025 --> 00:38:19.105
They sure taught you
many practical things.

00:38:25.825 --> 00:38:26.865
Are you doing this on purpose?

00:38:31.505 --> 00:38:32.905
Listen.

00:38:32.985 --> 00:38:35.665
Once we get back, make sure we follow
the due process for breaking in.

00:38:42.185 --> 00:38:43.385
‎FOR RENT

00:39:11.545 --> 00:39:14.505
The meat is all rotten.

00:39:14.585 --> 00:39:15.665
Look.

00:39:15.745 --> 00:39:17.185
They didn't even put the food away.

00:39:17.265 --> 00:39:18.825
Probably left in a hurry.

00:39:23.265 --> 00:39:24.425
I only have one.

00:39:38.545 --> 00:39:39.865
Poor thing.

00:39:52.745 --> 00:39:53.985
Why did they break the wall?

00:39:55.585 --> 00:39:56.705
Officer He.

00:39:58.585 --> 00:39:59.785
Size 37.

00:40:05.345 --> 00:40:06.305
DOUBLE FISH

00:40:07.985 --> 00:40:09.265
Double Fish Heels.

00:40:11.025 --> 00:40:12.105
Authenticity logo.

00:40:12.705 --> 00:40:14.065
It's expensive to get the real ones.

00:40:32.025 --> 00:40:33.625
Why did they break the wall?

00:40:35.265 --> 00:40:37.305
To move the cupboard out?

00:40:46.985 --> 00:40:47.825
So skinny.

00:40:48.785 --> 00:40:50.625
No wonder Xu Meng
could carry her father on her back.

00:40:52.025 --> 00:40:53.105
The father's teeth are quite unique.

00:40:59.985 --> 00:41:01.905
PENICILLIN V TABLETS

00:41:03.025 --> 00:41:03.905
That's odd.

00:41:03.985 --> 00:41:05.265
What is?

00:41:07.225 --> 00:41:11.065
I saw in the security footage
that her father was holding a cigarette.

00:41:11.145 --> 00:41:12.665
It looks like a cigarette.

00:41:13.425 --> 00:41:14.705
But he has a lung disease.

00:41:14.785 --> 00:41:16.025
Why would he be smoking?

00:41:17.625 --> 00:41:19.625
They have done weirder things.

00:41:19.705 --> 00:41:21.105
Perhaps he thought it wasn't worth it.

00:41:21.185 --> 00:41:23.105
Just smoke and drink however he wanted.

00:41:34.465 --> 00:41:35.745
HOUSEHOLD REGISTER

00:41:35.825 --> 00:41:36.665
HOUSEHOLD REGISTER, SAVINGS ACCOUNT

00:41:39.265 --> 00:41:41.585
REGISTER OF PERMANENT RESIDENT, XU ZHIHONG

00:41:41.665 --> 00:41:43.185
REGISTER OF PERMANENT RESIDENT, XU MENG

00:42:07.305 --> 00:42:08.825
Bowls?

00:42:08.905 --> 00:42:10.985
I've seen this brand in a mall in Beijing.

00:42:11.585 --> 00:42:14.345
This dress is probably
more expensive than this flat.

00:42:15.945 --> 00:42:19.505
It doesn't feel like something
Xu Meng would wear.

00:42:19.585 --> 00:42:20.865
It doesn't match her style.

00:42:22.145 --> 00:42:24.025
You sure know your fashion.

00:42:56.065 --> 00:42:57.185
Police!